Package: asterisk-chan-modemmanager
Architecture: any
Depends: ${asterisk:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: modemmanager
Description: ModemManager channel driver for Asterisk
 Asterisk channel driver that places and receives voice calls, SMS and
 MMS through ModemManager over D-Bus, with ALSA-direct audio, automatic
 USB-to-ALSA device correlation and per-modem init AT commands (e.g.
 Quectel AT+QPCMV=1,2 for voice over the USB audio function).
